data.description: Welcome to 4803 Roby Drive in the charming community of Archdale! This beautifully updated and meticulously maintained home is a true gem. With a host of attractive features and a location that offers convenient access to Trails to Creekside Park and the highway, it's a perfect place to call home. Ample space for your vehicles and extra storage with the 2 car garage and carport. Experience the luxury of renovated bathrooms, adding a touch of elegance to your daily routine. The kitchen boasts new cabinets, granite countertops, and modern appliances. The living room features a charming bricked fireplace. LVP flooring throughout the home. The expansive laundry room offers endless possibilities, from a craft space to additional storage. Improved insulation in the attic ensures energy efficiency and comfortable temperatures year-round. Enjoy your own private primary suite with a double vanity and a tiled walk-in shower. Recent HVAC system. This gem is a must see!
